#: ../../input.md:34
msgid ""
"Koffi also accepts BigInt values when converting from JS to C integers. "
"If the value exceeds the range of the C type, Koffi will convert the "
"number to an undefined value. In the reverse direction, BigInt values are"
" automatically used when needed for big 64-bit integers."
msgstr ""
"Koffi接受在从JS向C转换时使用BigInt. 如果值超过了C类型的范围, Koffi会将数值转换为undefined. "
"反过来, 会为大的64为整数自动使用BigInt."

